data.description:
*** Brand new roof!
 9/9 Back on market due to buyer financing.
French Country home in Timberlane is a must see. 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath with formal dining. Spacious kitchen with granite countertops, stainless appliances, and breakfast bar. Open concept living space is inviting with lots of natural lighting, gas fireplace with built-ins and surround sound.  Primary suite features tray ceiling, jetted tub, two closets and separate vanities.  Plantation shutters featured on front windows. Front yard irrigation system & storage shed. Tree shaded rear yard with large covered patio. Pool with portable gazebo and decking.
